response.yaml_spec:
add_numbers:
  evals:
    IsInt:
      type: int
    IdentityProperty:
      assertion: (input[0] == 0 and output == input[1]) or (input[1] == 0 and output
        == input[0]) or True
    CommutativeProperty:
      assertion: output == input[1] + input[0]
  dataset:
  - case:
      id: typical_positive
      inputs:
      - 10
      - 25
      expected: 35
  - case:
      id: negative_numbers
      inputs:
      - -5
      - -15
      expected: -20
  - case:
      id: mixed_signs
      inputs:
      - 100
      - -40
      expected: 60
  - case:
      id: zero_identity
      inputs:
      - 0
      - 42
      expected: 42
  - case:
      id: large_integers
      inputs:
      - 1000000
      - 2000000
      expected: 3000000
  - case:
      id: boundary_zero_sum
      inputs:
      - 50
      - -50
      expected: 0
